message: Focus heavily on tool usage. You can reliably get +30 items by using 'vial' on 'solid, magical' ingredients (like sunstone, mandrake root, unicorn horn) and by using 'filter' on 'liquid, mundane' ingredients (like tree sap, morning dew). Avoid combining ingredients; all my attempts resulted in significantly negative values, particularly when mixing 'magical' and 'mundane' features, or even different 'mundane' items. The maximum value I achieved was 30 per item, by using these specific tool-ingredient combinations.
